{"tid":1038200,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"葡萄牙球星 C 朗拿度雕像「超奇怪」，引發網民瘋狂 P 圖諷刺","createTime":"2019-02-26T13:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T13:50:52.000Z","uid":56984,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"184b2d8c9083fe5140cd48409a7076c802c42f7f","tid":1038200,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"相信大家都聽過葡萄牙著名球星 C 朗拿度的名字，他奪獎無數，更於去年的歐國盃帶領葡萄牙首次奪冠。而早前葡萄牙一個機場 Madeira Airport 更改名為「Cristiano Ronaldo International Airport」，並且展示了一個 C 朗的雕像作為紀念，亦邀請了該名球星出席，怎料揭幕的時候，全世界都嚇一跳，因為該雕像真是太醜樣 (與球星本人相差超遠) 了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n雕塑家 Emanuel Santos 本人則表示，C 朗有預先看過並接受有關雕塑，而且辯稱這是一種藝術品，不可能滿足所有人的品味和要求云云。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/183728/葡萄牙球星-c-朗拿度雕像「超奇怪」，引發網民瘋/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F183728%2F%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%89%99%E7%90%83%E6%98%9F-c-%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%BF%E5%BA%A6%E9%9B%95%E5%83%8F%E3%80%8C%E8%B6%85%E5%A5%87%E6%80%AA%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%98%8B%2F&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6cwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=989c6706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/183728/葡萄牙球星-c-朗拿度雕像「超奇怪」，引發網民瘋/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xv2joAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXv2joAV.jpg&h=6bd816f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0VwY9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0VwY9g.jpg&h=f4a102dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LbQtgVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbQtgVW.jpg&h=d4e85729&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Rcvvgu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Rcvvgu.jpg&h=ca59cc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXW8gWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXW8gWu.jpg&h=432fb0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http